NK039(ti)009:1: // dpal ldan lha mo'i bskang gsol bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)009:2: dpal phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)009:3: dpal ldan lha mo'i bskang gsol khyer bde la 'di skad do //
NK039(ti)009:5: yongs 'dus shing gis gnas mchog nas //
NK039(ti)009:6: rin chen mdzes pa'i pho brang na //
NK039(ti)009:7: bde ldan 'phrul gyi lding khang nang //
NK039(ti)009:8: 'gying bag tshul gyis gar mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)009:9: dbang phyug sras mo dung skyong ma //
NK039(ti)009:10: gdung bas spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)009:11: chibs su bong bu gwa dmar bcibs //
NK039(ti)009:12: ral gri ne'u le phyag na bsnams //
NK039(ti)009:13: sku la dur khrod chas kyis brgyan //
NK039(ti)009:14: dpal ldan lha mo gnas 'dir byon //
NK039(ti)009:15: byang shar thod pa'i sku mkhar ni //
NK039(ti)009:16: mi ro 'bum gyi khri steng na //
NK039(ti)009:17: drel nag rkang gsum chibs su bcibs //
NK039(ti)009:18: sku mdog nag mo re lde'i brgyan //
NK039(ti)009:19: phyag na khram bam shwa rde'u bsnams //
NK039(ti)009:20: bdud mo chen mo gnas 'dir gshegs //
NK039(ti)009:21: klu rnams dbang bsdud chu srin gdong //
NK039(ti)009:22: bka' yi blon po ba lam ma //
NK039(ti)009:23: las kyi pho nya khri sman ma //
NK039(ti)009:25: khyed kyi thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)009:26: sha khrag sna tshogs gtor ma la //
NK039(ti)009:27: snying sna sna tshogs rgyal mtshan btsug /
NK039(ti)009:28: dar zab mdzes pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK039(ti)009:29: sha chang sgog gtsang la sogs pa'i //
NK039(ti)009:30: mchod rdzas sna tshogs gcal du bkram //
NK039(ti)009:31: tshil chen dud pa sprin ltar 'khrigs //
NK039(ti)009:33: zhun chen mar me ta la la //
NK039(ti)009:34: thod rnga mi rkang dung la sogs //
NK039(ti)009:35: rol mo sna tshogs ti ri ri //
NK039(ti)009:36: snyan pa'i 'dzab bgrang ye re re //
NK039(ti)009:37: bdag gi dug gsum dbang gyur pas //
NK039(ti)009:38: dpal ldan lha mo 'khor bcas kyi //
NK039(ti)009:39: sku gsung thugs dang 'gal ba rnams //
NK039(ti)009:40: mchod sbyin 'di yis bskang gyur cig /
NK039(ti)009:41: rma bya 'jol sgeg ldan pa la //
NK039(ti)009:42: rin chen sna tshogs gshog pa can //
NK039(ti)009:43: rin chen 'bar bas spyi bo brgyan //
NK039(ti)009:44: ma cig gtso mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:45: de mo nag mo gser mig ma //
NK039(ti)009:46: yid bzhin nor bu'i sku la brgyan //
NK039(ti)009:47: yon tan du mar ldan pa 'dis //
NK039(ti)009:48: khol mo re ma ti yi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:49: nal phrug snying dang nal bus sha khrag dang //
NK039(ti)009:50: seng ge'i snying dang bya nag snying //
NK039(ti)009:51: nal phrug seng ge'i rgyal mtshan gyi //
NK039(ti)009:52: rje blon yongs kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:53: lha lug nag po spyi dkar dang //
NK039(ti)009:54: bya nag sgo nga dkar po la //
NK039(ti)009:55: yon tan sna tshogs ldan pa 'dis //
NK039(ti)009:56: ma mo yongs kyis thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:57: tsit+ta snying gi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:58: tshil chen dud pas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:59: mi rkang gling bus thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:60: g.yab dar nag pos thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:62: bskang ngo bskal pas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:63: phyag na rdo rje'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:64: ma h+aa d+ae ba'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:65: u ma d+ae ba'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:66: dpal ldan lha mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:67: ma h+aa k+aa la'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:68: bram ze mchog sred thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:69: e ka tsa ti'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:71: bskang ngo bskal pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:72: re lde mgo nyag thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:73: dran pa dbang byed thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:74: bdud mo re ma ti yi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:75: bka' bzhin las rnams sgrub pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)009:76: chu srin gdong gi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:77: dgra bgegs rtsad nas bcad pa'i ba lam nag mo'i
NK039(ti)009:78: bstan bsrung pho nya 'gyed pa'i khri sman sa le'i
NK039(ti)009:79: stag seng khyung dang bya rgod mgo //
NK039(ti)009:80: sgo ma bzhi yi smra bo lag ring la sogs pa'i //
NK039(ti)009:81: smra bsrung brgyad kyi dgra bgegs khram la 'debs pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)009:82: khram thogs brgyad kyi stong gsum ma lus nyul ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)009:83: bong zhon brgyad kyi bya ba'i las rnams bsgrub nam
NK039(ti)009:84: gru brgyad kyi 'khor du nag mo 'bum sde dang
NK039(ti)009:85: // srid pa'i ma mo stong gi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)009:86: sha za las kyi srin mo'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)009:87: stong phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi'i shar phyogs dkar mo
NK039(ti)009:88: 'bum gyi lho phyogs ser mo 'bum nub phyogs dmar
NK039(ti)009:89: mo 'bum byang phyogs ljang mo 'bum snang srid lha
NK039(ti)009:90: 'dre'i thugs brtan ma bcu gnyis ma mo bye ba'i
NK039(ti)009:91: bdud mo bye ba'i khyed kyi thugs dam bskang nas
NK039(ti)009:92: kyang // bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa yi //
NK039(ti)009:93: lus ngag yid gsum bya ba rnams //
NK039(ti)009:94: nyams par gyur pa ci mchis pa //
NK039(ti)009:95: dam can khyed la mthol lo bshags //
NK039(ti)009:96: phyin chad nyams pa mi bgyid 'tshal //
NK039(ti)009:97: khyed la phrin las las bcol ba ni //
NK039(ti)009:98: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba dang //
NK039(ti)009:99: sems can bde la 'god pa dang //
NK039(ti)009:100: nad gdon bar chad zhi ba dang //
NK039(ti)009:101: phas kyi rbod gtong bzlog pa dang //
NK039(ti)009:102: dam nyams dgra bgegs sgrol ba dang //
NK039(ti)009:103: bdag gi bsam pa'i don rnams kun //
NK039(ti)009:104: myur du 'grub pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)009:107: mi mngon dbyings nas bzhengs pa'i lha mo ni //
NK039(ti)009:108: dbang phyug sras mo dpal ldan dung skyong ma //
NK039(ti)009:109: srid gsum bdag mo dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)009:110: dpon g.yog 'khor bcas bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)009:111: thog ma'i dus nas dug gsum dbang gyur pas //
NK039(ti)009:112: lus ngag yid gsum sdig bgyis bgyid du brtsal //
NK039(ti)009:113: bgyis la yi rang mi dge sna tshogs bgyis //
NK039(ti)009:114: lha mo 'khor bcas khyed la mthol lo bshags //
NK039(ti)009:115: sku yi dam tshig yi dam lha dang 'gal //
NK039(ti)009:116: gsung gi dam tshig sngags kyi bzlas brjod g.yel //
NK039(ti)009:117: thugs kyi dam tshig gsang ba spel ba 'di //
NK039(ti)009:118: lha mo 'khor dang bcas la mthol lo bshags //
NK039(ti)009:119: sprul pa nal phrug bong drel ne'u le //
NK039(ti)009:120: gus pas mchod bstod ma byas khros shing rtsub //
NK039(ti)009:121: 'tshubs ma spangs shing rten rdzas spangs ba rnams //
NK039(ti)009:122: lha mo 'khor dang bcas la nya stong la sogs dus kyis byed pa la //
NK039(ti)009:123: bsnyen sgrub bskang ba dus kyi cho ga chags //
NK039(ti)009:124: shes shing khyad du gsod pa ci mchis pa //
NK039(ti)009:125: dam can bsrung ma'i tshogs la bsrung bya ma bsrung spang bya ma spangs dang //
NK039(ti)009:126: brten bya ma brten sgrub bya ma bsgrub pa'i //
NK039(ti)009:127: khas blangs dam bca' nyams pa ci mchis pa //
NK039(ti)009:128: bzod par gsol lo tshangs par stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)009:129: bdag gi dus rnams kun tu lha khyod dang //
NK039(ti)009:130: skad cig mi 'bral phrin las rnam bzhi yi //
NK039(ti)009:131: nam mkha'i mtha' mnyam sems can ma lus rnams //
NK039(ti)009:132: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa la 'khod par shog /
NK039(ti)009:133: yi ge brgya pa lan gsum mam bdun brjod par bya'o //
